<plot>George (George Shelton) wants to marry Lena Schmidt but her father disapproves. Tom (Tom Shelton) calls on old man Schmidt to fix things up for his friend George. He calls on the wrong Schmidt, who also has a daughter named Lena, and the two think Tom is there to ask for her hand for himself. Arrangements are made for a marriage but Tom and George think the intended bridegroom is George, as George does not know the wrong Schmidt was approached by Tom.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?223306</url></doc>
